TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, TM.CORP_CD, TD.STAT_CD, TD.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD, CASE WHEN R.RPT_TYP_CD=26 THEN 4 ELSE 3 END AS HVST_TYP_CD, MAX(TD.UPDT_TS) AS UPDT_TS FROM VRAP.TSNAP T INNER JOIN VRAP.TSNAP_DTL TD ON T.SNAP_ID=TD.SNAP_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THARVEST_QUE TQ ON TD.HVST_ID=TQ.HVST_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT R ON TQ.RPT_ID = R.RPT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY H ON R.HRCY_ID=H.HRCY_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TM ON T.MODEL_TYP_CD = TM.MODEL_TYP_CD WHERE TD.UPDT_TS> TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS') AND H.HRCY_TYP_CD=2 GROUP BY TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, TM.CORP_CD, TD.STAT_CD, TD.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD, R.RPT_TYP_CD WITH UR
